{
  "description": "A wide-angle view of the San Francisco Bay Bridge stretching across the San Francisco Bay. The bridge is a massive, multi-span suspension bridge with a distinctive orange hue, contrasting against the cool blue of the water and the overcast sky. In the background, the San Francisco skyline is visible, featuring a collection of high-rise buildings and the Transamerica Pyramid. Towards the right of the frame, rolling hills and distant mountains add depth to the scene. The water is choppy, creating subtle ripples and reflections. The sky is dominated by gray clouds, suggesting an overcast day.",
